"will appear in the app qube’s list of available applications. At this "
"point the snap will be persistent within the app qube and will receive "
"updates when the app qube is running."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-install-software.rst:327
#: f00757f78bf94cdc9c0dce0d33b154de
msgid "Autostarting Installed Applications"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-install-software.rst:329
