"If you want a desktop app to start automatically every time a qube starts"
" you can create a link to it in the ``~/.config/autostart`` directory of "
"the **app qube**. This might be useful for Qubes that you set to "
"automatically start on boot or for Qubes that have a set of apps you "
"typically use all day, such as a chat app."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/how-to-guides/how-to-install-software.rst:331
#: 98d442cd2da34552ab3fe19a0ab5db0c
msgid ""
